हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: When a single gunshot changes everything, Antonio finds himself behind bars and Isabella seemingly lost to a coma. Six months later, Isabella mysteriously awakens with no memory of her past—but something isn't right. As the cunning Stella slides into Isabella's identity, systematically draining the family fortune, a disoriented Isabella reaches out to the only person who might believe her: Antonio, the very man accused of shooting her. Following his cryptic directions to Detective Gonzalez, Isabella uncovers a shocking truth—she was never in a coma at all. Now, racing against time and deception, Isabella must piece together the fragments of her shattered reality before everything she once had vanishes forever.
